dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Noah Green. May I have your name please?
Hello, my name is Crystal Bennett.
Nice to meet you, Crystal. Can I have your date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, it's March twenty one, nine eight zero two.
Thank you, Crystal. Could you also provide the address associated with your policy?
Of course, it's six zero three Pine Street, Rockville, Maryland.
Thank you for the information, Crystal. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Noah.
You're welcome, Crystal. If you have any other questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Goodbye.
